One record identifies a user named 'KARYNA B' with a phone line active from May 16, 2014.
The financial liable party for the account(s) has been a customer since February 27, 2014, but their name is not disclosed in the provided text.
The records appear to be part of a law enforcement or investigative request, as indicated by the file numbering (EFTA00129314-17) and restrictive distribution notice.
